        <mj-column width="100%">
          <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff" font-size="18px">
            Thank you for choosing Hashtag Interactive!<br
              class="mobile-hide"
            />
            We're super stoked to start working with your team.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            padding-top="20px"
            align="center"
            color="#ffffff"
            font-size="18px"
          >
            To get you going, we've come up with a primer to help you through
            the<br class="mobile-hide" />
            Hashtag Interactive journey. We'll keep you updated on the progress
            of each<br class="mobile-hide" />
            of your projects and campaigns, but please don’t hesitate to keep in
            touch<br class="mobile-hide" />
            with anyone on our team for any questions or clarifications.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-image
