            src="images/your-project.png"
            alt="Your Project"
            align="left"
            width="232px"
          />
          <mj-text
            padding-top="5px"
            color="#ffffff"
            font-size="14px"
            text-transform="uppercase"
          >
            Duration | 6 months
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button mj-class="project-title"> Content Strategy </mj-button>
          <mj-text mj-class="project-desc">
            Planning the right content and messaging is crucial in ensuring that
            you achieve maximum outreach and engagement. Your content strategy
            with include key content pillars, themes and taglines to help
            communicate your brand more effectively.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button mj-class="project-title">
            Social |
            <span class="text-capitalize"
              >Facebook, LinkedIn &amp; Instragram</span
            >
          </mj-button>
          <mj-text mj-class="project-desc">
            We will work on expanding your reach and driving brand awareness -
            all of which ultimately impacts your sales conversion. We will work
            to establish a clear brand voice and content style guide that is
            consistent with Singapore Airshow's theme, diversifying content to
            include more interactive formats and drive engagement.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button mj-class="project-title">
            Reports and Analytics
          </mj-button>
          <mj-text mj-class="project-desc">
            We will provide monthly reports to keep watch on the metrics that
            matter most to your strategic initiatives.
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-group>
    </mj-section>
